narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I would. I have taken Chemistry multiple times, and I think this was probably the best time I learned it. It has to do with the professor and the great homework assignments.
For any student interested in taking general chemistry or required to take it, I would highly recommend taking this summer course instead of a full year course.
yes! a great condensed way to learn much information in little time
